How can I change the system to Chinese?

To change the system language to Chinese, you can follow the instructions in this article: [News Break'i başka bir dile ayarlayabilir miyim](https://help.newsbreak.com/hc/tr/articles/4415840753421-News-Break-i-ba%C5%9Fka-bir-dile-ayarlayabilir-miyim). Let me know if you need further assistance!

The 'My Profile' section can be found by signing into your NewsBreak account. Once you're signed in, look for the 'Me' tab at the bottom of the app. From there, you can access and edit your profile settings.
